16:03:13.000Z","msg":"黃子華2.0 不了"},{"pid":"8b0e5c357e1e423cb05d49f567acce76cfd570eb","tid":1854643,"uid":87428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:03:14.000Z","msg":"樓主以前成日曲線反達<br />\n到人真反 挽回唔到😂"},{"pid":"e7aff415f5c432779d8c518f188d38a4965a6513","tid":1854643,"uid":314983,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:06:23.000Z","msg":"達哥七宗罪去咗邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1a5eeie.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1a5eeie.gif&h=2bdcbef3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c463f7068edbd9b904067e4755a1475410f1f779","tid":1854643,"uid":19334,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e7aff415f5c432779d8c518f188d38a4965a6513","tid":1854643,"uid":314983,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:06:23.000Z","msg":"達哥七宗罪去咗邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1a5eeie.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1a5eeie.gif&h=2bdcbef3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:12:25.000Z","msg":"達哥七宗罪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 出賣 back up佬<br />\n<br />\n自己老番完人再屌人老番佢 好撚無恥<br />\n<br />\n早期你未紅 back up 佬冇錢收幫你宣傳又唔撚見你出聲<br />\n<br />\n利用完人就過橋抽板 唔該都冇聲<br />\n<br />\n2. 用老番window<br />\n<br />\n比兄弟踢爆用老番window<br />\n現場live果陣仲死撐扮傻仔話&lsquo;點解會咁？&lsquo;<br />\n之後見勢色唔對同兜唔到就扮晒死狗發文道歉<br />\n<br />\n3. 偷人潮文讀<br />\n<br />\n之前有個潮文作者話過有問題<br />\n達哥未得作者批准就用人地作品做商業用途<br />\n<br />\n4. 打機唔係為錢<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母打撚到搬去康城<br />\n收錢打埋d垃圾game <br />\n又話打機唔係為錢 自打嘴巴<br />\n<br />\n5. 奶共 ，親中，黃絲變藍絲<br />\n<br />\n入左中國公司之後<br />\n逢親大是大非都唔敢出聲<br />\n（黃之峰坐監，立法會投票）<br />\n<br />\n收淘寶錢雙十一買廣告就識！<br />\n<br />\n6. 成日用蝗語 同 人口filter<br />\n<br />\n呢個唔洗講啦 向班小學雞洗腦"},{"pid":"eaa72677f665edf449e401894781f7c2bb36420a","tid":1854643,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ad44d83c36b7112a4aa97e4efd9b